OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear skies
OL,6,Fto end the day for most. Overnight,
OL,7,Fpatchy low cloud moves across large
OL,8,Fparts of the region. The wind eases
OL,9,Fslightly inland, but remaining breezy
OL,10,Falong the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FCloud will burn off to give
OL,13,Fsunny spells, sunshine turning hazy by
OL,14,Flate afternoon with showers possible
OL,15,Fin the evening. Feeling very warm or
OL,16,Fhot inland, but cooler near coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
