OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FHazy
OL,6,Fsunshine during the days, with showers
OL,7,Fpossible, perhaps thundery at times,
OL,8,Fwith the greatest risk on Wednesday.
OL,9,FWind easing by Thursday. Becoming very
OL,10,Fwarm or hot inland once more.
